SPAdes
Genome assembler for single-cell and isolates data sets
Version: see VERSION

Developed in Algorithmic Biology Lab of St. Petersburg Academic University of the Russian Academy of Sciences.

Current SPAdes contributors:

    Dmitry Antipov,
    Anton Bankevich.
    Alexey Gurevich,
